column5: This year just the 4 of us fishing from Thursday to Sunday. Weatherwise it looks promising. Gear is packed and awaiting the arrival of the other 3 from Niagara at 7 a.m.  Will post a report when I return.  Now if I can just get to sleep.  By they way, who here can identify my avatar?
good luck man... we'll be up there sometime friday for the weekend.. if you see a red lund with 4 dudes, not catching anything, it'll prolly be us
Have fun  Is that John Cleese in the background?  Joey
We're staying at Cozy Cove. There will be a 14' red lund with a 25hp Honda and 19'black and gold Lund with a130hp Honda. I'll keep an eye out for you BS2K
Yes..I don't know how you came to that conclusion as he is hard to see. Can you tell me the character name in the foreground?
Good Luck and be safe out there.MTP
Manuel Superbly!!  What do I win
Sorry no prize other than the smile when remembering the crazy antics at Fawlty Towers. One of the funniest shows ever shown on TV.
second time typing this reply *stupid keyboard*  i'll keep my eye out for ya.. we're staying around the corner at sandy bay...
Yep, it was dang funny that's for sure.  Joey
